name: tracking_shuffled_objects_five_objects_11
task:
Write the answer to the following question to a file called answer.txt: Alice, Bob, Claire, Dave, and Eve are playing a game. At the start of the game, they are each holding a ball: Alice has a brown ball, Bob has a black ball, Claire has a red ball, Dave has a pink ball, and Eve has a blue ball.
As the game progresses, pairs of players trade balls. First, Claire and Bob swap balls. Then, Claire and Eve swap balls. Then, Bob and Claire swap balls. Then, Dave and Claire swap balls. Finally, Alice and Dave swap balls. At the end of the game, Claire has the
Options:
(A) brown ball
(B) black ball
(C) red ball
(D) pink ball
(E) blue ball
